Miss
Crawford
thought
she
had
never
seen
a
prettier
consciousness.
"My
dear
child,"
said
she,
laughing,
"what
are
you
afraid
of?
Do
you
think
Henry
will
claim
the
necklace
as
mine,
and
fancy
