to
explain
my
errand.
You
will
find
the
beginning
of
a
note
to
yourself;
but
I
can
now
speak
my
business,
which
is
merely
to
beg
your
acceptance
of
this
little
trifle
a
chain
for
William's
cross.
You
ought
to
have
had
it
a
week
ago,
but
there
has
been
a
delay
from
my
brother's
not
being
in
