I
should
have
thought
it
a
gross
violation
of
duty
and
respect.
You
are
not
to
be
judged
by
the
same
rule.
You
do
not
owe
me
the
duty
of
a
child.
But,
Fanny,
if
your
heart
can
acquit
you
of
ingratitude
"
He
ceased.
Fanny
was
by
this
time
crying
so
bitterly
that,
angry
as
he
was,
he
would
not
press
that
article
