a
gentleman,
and
now
I
am
sure
she
was
wrong.
By
the
bye,
Flora
Ross
was
dying
for
Henry
the
first
winter
she
came
out.
But
were
I
to
attempt
to
tell
you
of
all
the
women
whom
I
have
