absence,
to
be
given
to
Northamptonshire,
and
was
coming,
the
happiest
of
lieutenants,
because
the
latest
made,
to
shew
his
happiness
and
describe
his
uniform.
He
came;
and
he
would
have
been
delighted
to
shew
his
uniform
there
