"I
have
to
inform
you,
my
dearest
Fanny,
that
Henry
has
been
down
to
Portsmouth
to
see
you;
that
he
had
a
delightful
walk
with
you
to
the
dockyard
last
Saturday,
and
one
still
more
to
be
dwelt
on
the
next
day,
on
the
ramparts;
when
the
balmy
air,
the
