but
but
but
Yours
affectionately."
"I
had
almost
forgot
(it
was
Edmund's
fault:
he
gets
into
my
head
more
than
does
me
good)
one
very
material
thing
I
had
to
say
from
Henry
and
myself
I
mean
about
our
taking
you
back
into
Northamptonshire.
My
dear
little
creature,
do
not
stay
at
Portsmouth
to
lose
your
pretty
