They
are
very
fond
of
her;
but
I
am
sure
she
does
not
love
them
as
she
loves
you.
When
I
think
of
her
great
attachment
to
you,
indeed,
and
the
whole
of
her
judicious,
upright
conduct
as
a
sister,
she
appears
a
very
different
creature,
capable
of
everything
noble,
and
I
am
ready
to
blame
myself
for
a
too
harsh
construction
of
a
