and
how
to
endeavour
to
weaken
her
hold
on
my
heart,
and
in
the
course
of
a
few
years
but
I
am
writing
nonsense.
Were
I
refused,
I
must
bear
it;
and
till
I
am,
I
can
never
cease
to
try
for
her.
This
is
the
truth.
The
only
question
is
how?
What
may
be
the
likeliest
