to
Miss
Bertram.
You
will
wish
to
hear
my
opinion
of
Maria's
degree
of
comfort
as
a
wife.
There
is
no
appearance
of
unhappiness.
I
hope
they
get
on
pretty
well
together.
I
dined
twice
in
Wimpole
Street,
and
might
have
been
there
