To
have
him
still
the
acquaintance,
the
flirt
perhaps,
of
Mrs.
Rushworth!
She
was
mortified.
She
had
thought
better
of
him.
Happily,
however,
she
was
not
left
to
weigh
and
decide
between
opposite
